# Implementation Plan - Admin Portal Issues & Enhancement Fixes

This plan outlines the changes needed to resolve the 6 issues reported in the Karayabandhu Pvt Ltd portfolio and admin portal.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Database Schema Update:**
> - We will update `ApplicationSchema` and `CertificateClaimSchema` in [db.js](file:///c:/Users/hp/Desktop/work/karyabandhu_portfolio/Karayabandhu%20Pvt%20Ltd%20project/app/lib/db.js) to store a `read` boolean (default: `false`).
> - We will add `fileUrl` to the `credentials` object in `ApplicationSchema` to track the uploaded resume path.
> - This schema change is fully backwards-compatible (existing entries without these fields will default to `read: false` or blank `fileUrl`).

> [!NOTE]
> **New Endpoint:**
> - We will create a new public route `/api/upload-resume` to allow candidates to upload their PDF/Word resumes during application submission (since the existing `/api/upload` is restricted to authenticated admins).

