  3. Verify that navigating to the "LMS Certificates" tab resets the certificate notification badge count.
  4. Scroll down long lists of items and check that the sidebar remains sticky in the viewport.
  5. Try delete actions and verify the beautiful custom confirm modal displays instead of the browser alert.
